short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Change the color of your GitHub contribution graph

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
After falling in love with GitHub's Halloween theme, it made absolute sense to create this extension!

This extension allows you to change the color theme of your GitHub contribution graph.
